    "description": "《龙之宝藏》是一款Roguelike动作游戏，主要采用单人跑团爬塔的游戏机制，配合20面骰子生成不同的事件结果对角色造成多种影响，游戏的变身武器有15种，常规武器有7种，目前游戏有上千种外貌组合和外观样式，55种遗物改变角色的战斗能力，25种事件每种世界分为成功，失败，大成功，大失败等结果，游戏的战斗玩法是不断地打败boss，获得相应的变身能力，之后通过组合遗物和不同的变身能力继续通关地城，<br><br>一、游戏地图机制——单人跑团+爬塔<br>游戏的非战斗常规跑团爬塔模式是类似桌游的20面骰子系统驱动，20面骰子产生的结果分别为成功，失败，大成功，大失败。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/c753d50de6a56d454d1ce29a4a2671fb.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/c753d50de6a56d454d1ce29a4a2671fb.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/c753d50de6a56d454d1ce29a4a2671fb.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>二、游戏战斗玩法——不断打败强力敌人获得稀有遗物，搭配多种遗物效果组合构建自己的战斗方式，举例来说像配合弹反遗物的专注弹反的战斗方式，配合防御的反伤战斗方式，配合极限闪避的子弹时间战斗方式，配合基础攻击暴击加速的暴走式战斗方式。<br>下面例子为暴走式战斗方式<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/204878806c7601d06bc3c90be724a8aa.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/204878806c7601d06bc3c90be724a8aa.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/204878806c7601d06bc3c90be724a8aa.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>下面例子为弹反类遗物战斗方式<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/5b9586f41be79658f8d54255d465789f.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/5b9586f41be79658f8d54255d465789f.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/5b9586f41be79658f8d54255d465789f.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>三、游戏变身玩法——通过打败强力的特殊敌人，可获得敌人的专属武器，使用后可改变角色的战斗模式，彻底变身为你打败的强力敌人，举例来说，常规武器只有7种近战武器，但是变身武器种有15种，其中还包括远程武器弓箭，法师的法杖，忍者的苦无和忍刀等等。<br>法师变身<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/65f5437b63b3d2a3111604b56dbb7cd8.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/65f5437b63b3d2a3111604b56dbb7cd8.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/65f5437b63b3d2a3111604b56dbb7cd8.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>忍者变身<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/f0bff4e1bc565ba9ce5945299fbec7dd.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/f0bff4e1bc565ba9ce5945299fbec7dd.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/f0bff4e1bc565ba9ce5945299fbec7dd.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>弓箭手变身<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/e4c43a9d68870ed5e1cfdd7969042c6b.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/e4c43a9d68870ed5e1cfdd7969042c6b.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/e4c43a9d68870ed5e1cfdd7969042c6b.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>刺客变身<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/29fcfe1c53554144706c23b8f1b3ff8e.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/29fcfe1c53554144706c23b8f1b3ff8e.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/29fcfe1c53554144706c23b8f1b3ff8e.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>四、自定义装备和外观系统——游戏有多种装备和外观可自定义角色的样子，每一局给你不一样的体验，每一把武器的前后摇和手感都有很大的差异，哪怕是同类的武器，比如都是大锤，手感也会有些许差异。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/cbe45377de2ca044479bfebe69353bac.poster.avif?t=1679711063\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/cbe45377de2ca044479bfebe69353bac.webm?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237800/extras/cbe45377de2ca044479bfebe69353bac.mp4?t=1679711063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>五、死亡传承系统——游戏保留Ruguelike游戏的一贯传统，角色死亡后会重置角色的全部信息，但是可以在死亡后用剩余金币解锁传承系统，此类传承可永久保留，并且全游戏全存档都会生效。",
